      <section eId="sec_399_ZZZZZ*2">
        <num>399-ZZZZZ*2</num>
        <heading>Use of preferred name and pronouns</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_399_ZZZZZ*2__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>willfully and repeatedly fail to use a customer's preferred name\nand/or preferred pronouns after being clearly informed of the preferred\nname and/or preferred pronouns pursuant to subdivision two of this\nsection; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_399_ZZZZZ*2__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>require a customer to specify their sexual orientation or gender\nidentity or expression in order to use their preferred name and/or\npreferred pronouns.\n  * NB There are 2 ยง 399-zzzzz's\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
